Test::XML version
=================

This module provides tools for testing code which deals with XML.  These
tools are compatible with the Test::More and Test::Simple modules.  At
present, there is generic XML comparison support, as well as modules for
dealing with XML::SAX, XML::Twig and XML::XPath handlers.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Test::More
  XML::SemanticDiff

These modules are not required, but will provide more functionality.

  XML::SAX
  XML::Twig
  XML::XPath

